      "title": "The number of people infected with Covid is increasing",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The number of Covid infected people reported from Sri Lanka is showing a gradual increase. Thus, 131 Covid-infected people have been identified today. The number of Covid-infected people identified yesterday is 119.",
        "Thus, more than 100 Covid-infected people have been reported on two consecutive days. However, no Covid deaths have been reported today.",
        "The number of Covid-infected people identified in Sri Lanka so far has increased to 665,379."
      ],
